<author>Ngama</author>
<title>Ei Khawtuoh Pathien</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka Pathien Aw, ei khawtuohpa,
 Na lam ka mansak nung inle;
 Na lungsietna Aw hawih takin,
 Na hehpihna thu lopi chun;
 Ka lunggil sung a fang viel ie (2) DS

[V2]
 2. Na vangsaknan lei Na khuha,
 Thilhih theihnan Na dawm kanga;
 A chungah kei le ka leng ie,
 Ka gitloh ziekin Lal Isu,
 Thah in A um kalvari ah (2) DS

[V3]
 3. Na hehpihna a thuk taluoi,
 Mihiem chitnan a pha zo puoi;
 Ka neu taluoi puong seng puo'ng ka,
 Ka puma ka kipiek khel chu;
 Hih theih dang ka nei puoi Lalpa (2) DS

[V4]
 4. Keile Lalpa, keia dingin,
 Na cha neih sun Na hun sawl hi;
 Ka theihtawp suohin pang ingka,
 Ka thil bangkim hun taihsan in;
 Ka pumin hung kipieng ka ie (2) DS

[V5]
 5. Ka leisiet hinkhuo a beih tieng,
 Na thagau in ei pui zelin;
 Nanga ding maiin hing ingka,
 Ka hinna thanmuol a lem tieng;
 Kumkhuo'n Na kawmah um tangka (2) DS</lyrics>
</song>